{"tid":1719973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係無限期罷工未","createTime":"2019-11-14T08:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:41:15.000Z","uid":129529,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f8872c2e7e2fa0d2367406950bba02bde6f705ed","tid":1719973,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"勇武係有盡頭 點打都好 武力始終唔係對等 <br />\n<br />\n有人受傷 有人死 有人被自殺 強姦 <br />\n<br />\n如果你地真係唔想見到再發生 <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以徹徹底底無限期罷工<br />\n<br />\n我只係一個學生 不及你地工作緊既大人有影響力<br />\n<br />\n去到今時今日 我睇三罷既group 夾埋都冇十萬人 <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以俾我睇想贏既決心<br />\n<br />\n成日話經濟攬炒 <br />\n<br />\n玩魔法可以燒起啲野 再加啲燃料落去仲會仲即變更大<br />\n<br />\n而成年人既罷工正正係加燃料落攬炒到 加速攬炒<br />\n<br />\n如果連罷工都做唔到 呢場革命只會終結<br />\n<br />\n而香港人都不過如此"},{"pid":"0b085093ffb67349e56b0397d72ba3e72d1f0191","tid":1719973,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:15:26.000Z","msg":"鄭立：大學係「要塞」 唔係防守而係攻擊據點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718775</a>"},{"pid":"dc1e472495ab74ff1b766f036e7b32cd2d869b1e","tid":1719973,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d12f47a6037048813a8eede43616fa600bb23b40","tid":1719973,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72a17dabc77ea02d42c77b21a455f39e3bea6e47","tid":1719973,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"事實已證明自願罷工係無可能<br />\n只能靠被罷工"},{"pid":"f935bd5cead433a9faba93f026fc669e6c1fbd69","tid":1719973,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:18:10.000Z","msg":"內戰都打埋仲返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7067cdf4ac39cc3123a683b1e5bdcc6f57617c61","tid":1719973,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"雖然由個學生叫人罷工 個